NK016(ma)002:0: dpa' bo tshogs kyi rnam rol zhes bya ba'i tik+ka 'dod don lam khyer gyi dabu'o //
NK016(ma)002:2: gu ru d+he wa d+aa ki la na mo /
NK016(ma)002:3: chos dbyings rnam dag ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK016(ma)002:4: 'gags med sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor ston //
NK016(ma)002:5: mdzad pa phrin las gdul bya'i dpal du shar //
NK016(ma)002:6: tshogs kyis gtso bo de la mi phyed 'dud //
NK016(ma)002:7: tshogs gnyis rab rdzogs dam tshig chags nyams bskang //
NK016(ma)002:8: sgrib gnyis rnam dag las rnams myur du 'grub //
NK016(ma)002:9: dus min 'chi ba bzlog tshe bar chad sel //
NK016(ma)002:10: rbod gtong ltas ngan ye 'drog sna tshogs bzlog /
NK016(ma)002:11: 'dod yon lam khyer gsang sngags che yon rdzogs //
NK016(ma)002:12: myur skyob bde skyor 'di ni byang chub lam //
NK016(ma)002:13: mthar thug longs spyod rdzogs sku thob las che //
NK016(ma)002:14: de phyir gsang sngags sgor zhugs rnal 'byor rnams //
NK016(ma)002:15: 'di la thugs dam brtson 'grus nan tan mdzod //
NK016(ma)002:16: de phyir tshogs kyis dpa' bo rnam rol shad //
NK016(ma)002:17: tshogs kyi mchod pa'i skabs 'di la //
NK016(ma)002:18: thog mar rnal 'byor pho mo rnams brda dang brda'i lan la mkhas dgos /
NK016(ma)002:19: ma mkhas na tshogs kyi mchod pa'i nang na 'dug ra med pa rgya gar ba rnams kyis bshad /
NK016(ma)002:20: rgyud sde'i nang nas kyang gsungs /
NK016(ma)002:21: de la brda la bzhi ste /
NK016(ma)002:26: dang po brda'i dgos pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:27: rdo rje'i mched lcam dang rdo rje'i spun du gyur pa'i dgos pa yod de /
NK016(ma)002:28: de'ang bod kyis rnal 'byor pa gcig gis rus pa'i
NK016(ma)002:29: rgyan cha drug thogs nas spyod pa la song ba'i
NK016(ma)002:30: dus su / rgya gar nas rnal 'byor pa gcig byung nas de gnyis brda sprad de /
NK016(ma)002:31: gcig gis dgyes pa rdo rje'i brda byas pas /
NK016(ma)002:32: gcig gis gdan bzhi'i sgo nas brda byas nas brda ma mthun nas /
NK016(ma)002:33: rdo rje'i spun du ma gyur /
NK016(ma)002:34: brda mthun na rdo rje'i spun du gyur /
NK016(ma)002:35: rnal 'byor ma dang brda mthun na rdo rje'i lcam 'brel lam rnal 'byor ming sring du 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)002:38: rnal 'byor ming sring brtse gdung ldan //
NK016(ma)002:41: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK016(ma)002:44: gsang sngags kyi chos gsang sgrogs su mi 'gyur ba'i dgos ched yod de /
NK016(ma)002:45: gsang phyir brda dag sna tshogs gsungs /
NK016(ma)002:47: gnyis pa brda'i nges tshig ni /
NK016(ma)002:48: rnal 'byor pa rang gi go zhing /
NK016(ma)002:49: gzhan gyis mi go bas na brda zhes bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:50: dper na lkug pa'i 'dzub brda bzhin no //
NK016(ma)002:51: gsum pa brda'i dus tshod ni /
NK016(ma)002:52: spyod pa spyod pa'i dus dang dbang bskur ba'i dus dang /
NK016(ma)002:54: bskyed rdzogs bsgom pa'i thun mtshams kyis dus de rnams la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:58: lus kyis brda la sor mo gcig ston pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:59: legs par 'ong ngam zhes dris pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:60: de'i lan du sor mo gnyis bshib nas bstan te legs par 'ong zhes pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:61: g.yon pa'i mthe mo bcang ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:63: de'i lan du ngag tu ra ti bya ba ni khams bde zhes pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:64: bum dbang ma thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa mi 'ong bas /
NK016(ma)002:65: gsang dbang thob pa ma dris pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:66: srin lag dang mathe'u chung bcad nas ston te /
NK016(ma)002:67: byang sems dkar dmar gnyis po de lce thog tu bzhag gam dris pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:68: de'i lan du mgrin pa rab tu bstan te /
NK016(ma)002:69: thig le dkar dmar mgrin par longs spyod ces pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:70: dbang gsum pa thob bam dris pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:72: de'i len ni mathe'u chung bstan ste gsum pa a
NK016(ma)002:73: cang che te bzhi ba'i don la reg go zhes
NK016(ma)002:74: pa'o // dbang rdzogs kyang lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes rtogs sam dris pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:76: de'i len ni 'dzub mo ston no //
NK016(ma)002:77: de ni byang chub sems kyis rten rtsa'i man ngag dris pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:78: go ste thod bstan pa ni brda /
NK016(ma)002:79: de'i len ni rdo rje rtse gsum gyis phyag rgya bstan te rtsa gsum gyi ngo bo /
NK016(ma)002:81: byang chub sems kyis man ngag shes sam dri ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:82: gang zhig nu ma ston pa ni nu ma nas 'o ma 'bab pa ltar /
NK016(ma)002:83: 'o ma dang 'dra ba'i kun rdzob byang chub sems de gang na gnas zhes dri ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:84: de'i len ni skra mtshams bzlog nas ston pa ste
NK016(ma)002:85: byang chub sems de phal cher mchog gsang 'og ma
NK016(ma)002:86: nag nas zhes bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:87: gang zhig sa ni ston pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:88: sa gzhi 'di la thams cad longs spyod cing brten par byed /
NK016(ma)002:89: de dang 'dra bar byang chub kyis sems de phyag
NK016(ma)002:90: rgya mo la brten nas longs spyod zhes dri ba'o
NK016(ma)002:91: // len de la mkha' ni rab tu bstan lag pa nam mkha' la kyog kyog byas te /
NK016(ma)002:92: phyag rgya mo la brten nas longs spyod do ces so //
NK016(ma)002:96: brda skad dang gsum gsum re yod /
NK016(ma)002:98: rgya gar skad du su ra /
NK016(ma)002:100: brda skad du ba la'am thabs rdzas /
NK016(ma)002:103: brda skad du pad+ma b+ha dza ni /
NK016(ma)002:104: rgya gar skad du ka p+aa la /
NK016(ma)002:106: brda skad du tri pa ta ru /
NK016(ma)002:107: rgya gar skad du da ma ru /
NK016(ma)002:110: rgya gar skad du +aa pa ra mi b+h+ya /
NK016(ma)002:112: brda'i skad du ka ko la /
NK016(ma)002:113: rgya gar skad bod skad gnyis ka la pad+ma de la sogs pa'i brda chos mang ngo //
NK016(ma)002:114: da ni tshogs kyis mchod pa rang la /
NK016(ma)002:118: dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs de la /
NK016(ma)002:121: 'byor ldan yo byad kyis tshogs de longs spyod pa'am mchod pas tshogs mchod ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:123: slob dpon pad+mas don bcu gcig gis bstan te /
NK016(ma)002:124: byed pa'i dus bstan pa dang gcig byed pa'i gnas bstan pa dang gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:125: rgyu'i yo byad bstan pa dang gsum /
NK016(ma)002:126: sngon 'gro'i bar chad bstan pa dang bzhi /
NK016(ma)002:127: rnal 'byor pas spyod lam bstan pa dang lnga /
NK016(ma)002:128: yo byad byin gyis brlabs pa drug /
NK016(ma)002:129: ting 'dzin bskyed rim gzhung bsrang ba dang bdun /
NK016(ma)002:130: tshogs kyis mchod pa 'bul ba dang brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:131: tshogs la rol ba dang dgu /
NK016(ma)002:132: lhag ma gtor skyongs bro'i las bstan pa dang bcu /
NK016(ma)002:133: rjes kyis bya ba bstan pa dang bcu gnyis so //
NK016(ma)002:134: da res 'dir dam pa bde bar gshegs pa'i bzhed
NK016(ma)002:135: pa'i tshogs mchod 'di la don rnam pa drug ste
NK016(ma)002:136: / sngon du bya ba'i rim pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:138: mtshams bcad cing dal sprul pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:139: tshogs byin gyis brlabs cing byin dbab pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:140: mchod cing rol pa'i cho ga dang /
NK016(ma)002:141: bkra shis brjod cing lhag pa'i las bya ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:142: de'ang sngon du bya ba'i rim pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:149: khrid la sogs pa'i dus dang /
NK016(ma)002:160: gnam stong dang 'di rnams kyis dus ni ma dang mkha' 'gro 'du ba'i dus yin pas /
NK016(ma)002:161: nyi ma thal phyin chad la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:165: dgon gnas byin rlabs can la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:166: cung zad ye shes la dbang ba'i gang zag gis /
NK016(ma)002:167: u rgyan la sogs pa'i dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad dam /
NK016(ma)002:168: dza len ng+ha ra la sogs pa'i gnas nyi shu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK016(ma)002:169: drag shul can gyi gnas rnams 'grim nas tshogs dang spyod pa /
NK016(ma)002:170: khyad par du dbye dgos pas /
NK016(ma)002:171: gsang sngags bla med kyis rgyud sde rnams kyi nang nas gsungs so //
NK016(ma)002:172: 'dir rang re dgon gnas dben par man+dala ci rigs pa phyi bdar byas la /
NK016(ma)002:173: lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i tshom bu bkram la /
NK016(ma)002:185: tshogs kyi zhal zas kyis rnam pa ser sna ma song ba'i yo byad dang /
NK016(ma)002:187: phyag rgya mo mtshan nyid dang ldan pa la khrus
NK016(ma)002:188: byas nas rgyan btags la g.yon du bzhag ces gsang
NK016(ma)002:189: sngags kyis rgyud sde nas gsungs kyang /
NK016(ma)002:190: 'dir re zhig ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya mo la brten par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:196: ting ting shag la sogs pa'i sgra snyan dang /
NK016(ma)002:198: du khrod kyi chas la sogs pa rnams bshams /
NK016(ma)002:199: ces slob dpon pad+mas gsungs so //
NK016(ma)002:200: 'dir dam pa yab sras kyis tshogs kyi zhal zas bshams lugs ni /
NK016(ma)002:201: dza gad dang pany+tsa sbyar ba'i snod gcig dal gyis nub phyogs su bzhag go //
NK016(ma)002:202: sha'i rigs thams cad dal gyi lho phyogs su bzhag go //
NK016(ma)002:203: shing thog dang zho phrum la sogs pa thams cad ni dal gyi shar phyogs su bzhag go //
NK016(ma)002:204: zla rdzogs ni tshogs bshos zla gam du byas la byang phyogs bzhag go //
NK016(ma)002:205: de dag thams cad la dar gyi zhal kheb byas la mi mngon par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:207: 'dir phyag len la gral thabs sam gru chad bzhi la man ngag bzhin du bshams /
NK016(ma)002:208: bsang chu sman raka rnams phyag len ltar bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:209: khyad par du tshogs rdzas la /
NK016(ma)002:210: bza' ba'i rigs thams cad thabs kyi rdzas yin pas g.yas su bzhag /
NK016(ma)002:211: btung ba'i rigs thams cad shes rab kyi ngo bo yin pas g.yon du bzhag go //
NK016(ma)002:212: rgya gar ba rnams kyi tshogs rdzas bshams lugs ni /
NK016(ma)002:213: gsang sngags rang gzhung gis lta spyod dang mthun pa yin te /
NK016(ma)002:214: tshogs rdzas bzang ngan thams cad snod gcig tu spung nas byin gyis brlabs /
NK016(ma)002:215: tshogs la rol ba'i dus su /
NK016(ma)002:217: yug sha khyad med par za ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:218: gzhan yang sku gsung thugs kyis rten byin rlabs can rnams bkram /
NK016(ma)002:225: gnas khang brgyan cing shin tu yid du 'ong bar bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:226: de nas las kyi spyod lam bstan pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:227: rgya gar ba rnams kyi tshogs kyi gnas khang du
NK016(ma)002:228: bla ma dang dbyug pa sngon po phyar ba 'bag
NK016(ma)002:230: mig ya gcig gnam la blta ba /
NK016(ma)002:231: ya gcig sa la blta ba /
NK016(ma)002:232: lag na dbyug pa sngon po 'dom gang ba gcig bzung ba /
NK016(ma)002:233: gos sngon po gon pa gcig dang /
NK016(ma)002:234: las kyis he ru ka bya ba bya bzhag byed pa'i mi gcig dang gsum nang du bsdad /
NK016(ma)002:235: gzhan dpa' bo dpa' mo thams cad phyi rol du 'gro la khrus bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:236: der dbyug sngon gyis sgo bcad nas /
NK016(ma)002:237: sgo rgyab tu bsdad mi rnams kyis nang nas dpon
NK016(ma)002:238: gcig gis sgo bsrung la me tog phul bas gsol
NK016(ma)002:239: ba gdab ste / kye khro bo sngon po mdzes pa che //
NK016(ma)002:240: khyod ni dam tshig yid du 'ong //
NK016(ma)002:241: nor bu rin chen spyi bcing pas //
NK016(ma)002:242: phyag na dbyug pa bsnams pa 'dis //
NK016(ma)002:243: bdag nyid 'khor ba las bsgral phyir //
NK016(ma)002:244: gsang sngags gsang ba'i da la 'dir //
NK016(ma)002:246: bzang ba'i sgo 'di rnam par phyes //
NK016(ma)002:248: gsang sngags kyi brda dang brda'i len du ma shes na /
NK016(ma)002:249: dbyug sngon gyis dbyug pa brgyab nas nang du mi btang ngo //
NK016(ma)002:250: len theb na nang du btang ste /
NK016(ma)002:251: sgo srung gis len byin pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:252: h'u theg dman nyan thos log lta can //
NK016(ma)002:253: mu stegs la sogs bskrad par byed //
NK016(ma)002:254: skal dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor rnams //
NK016(ma)002:255: nang du rnam par btang bar bya //
NK016(ma)002:257: de'i dus su gu gul gyis dud pas bdug /
NK016(ma)002:258: khro bo'i drag sngags bzlas la /
NK016(ma)002:259: phyir 'brang gi bgegs bskrad par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:260: de nas gral la 'khod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:261: thog mar gdan la 'khod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:262: ras la ro'i gzugs bris la /
NK016(ma)002:264: yang na stag gis spags pa can dang /
NK016(ma)002:265: yang na dur khrod kyis ro ras la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:266: gdan de'i steng du dpa' bo g.yas gral /
NK016(ma)002:268: yang na zung sdeb du 'khod do //
NK016(ma)002:269: de nas las kyi rdo rjes /
NK016(ma)002:270: rnal 'byor pho mo rnams gsan du gsol //
NK016(ma)002:271: bla ma la ma zhus pa'i spyod pa bag med pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:272: ngag 'dzin rten gyis dug lnga dang 'brel ba'i gtam dang /
NK016(ma)002:273: kha na ma tho ba'i ngag 'khyal dang /
NK016(ma)002:274: yid nyon mongs pa dang 'brel ba'i bsam pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:277: log par lta ba thams cad spang la /
NK016(ma)002:278: dag pa'i snang bas bla ma la sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes nye bar bzhag la /
NK016(ma)002:279: yan lag bdun pa rgyas bsdus ci rigs pa bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:280: de nas yang las kyi rdo rjes phyag 'tshal nas /
NK016(ma)002:281: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen pos dbu mdzad /
NK016(ma)002:282: rnal 'byor pho mo thams cad rang rang gi thugs dam la mnyam par bzhag par zhu /
NK016(ma)002:283: rnal 'byor pho mo thams cad kyis gnas gsum du bdud rtsi'i thig le re re byas la /
NK016(ma)002:284: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs /
NK016(ma)002:286: rus pa'i rgyan cha dpal gyi chas brgyad rnams kyis mnga' gsol zhing rtags gdab bo //
NK016(ma)002:287: de nas las dang po la bar chad 'ong dogs pa'i ched du bsrung ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:288: skabs 'dir dam pa bde bar gshegs pas /
NK016(ma)002:289: rdo rje slob dpon nas bzung ste /
NK016(ma)002:290: thams cad kyi dbu la me tog gi phreng ba re re gdag gsungs /
NK016(ma)002:291: rgya gar ba rnams kyi phyag len la /
NK016(ma)002:292: tshogs la ma byon pa'i dus su rnal 'byor pho mo rnams la me tog 'grim dgos par bshad /
NK016(ma)002:294: brda dang brda'i len la mi mkhas pa'am /
NK016(ma)002:295: thugs mi skabs na me tog mi len no //
NK016(ma)002:297: me tog len nas tshogs kyi gtso bo la 'bul dgos par bshad /
NK016(ma)002:298: des sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa de song nas /
NK016(ma)002:299: spyi don gnyis pa gsol ba gdab pa skabs 'dir gsungs kyang /
NK016(ma)002:300: phyag len la 'og dngos gzhi'i skabs su bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:301: spyi don gsum pa mtshams bcad cing dal sprul pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:302: yan lag brgyad pa nas bzung ste /
NK016(ma)002:303: yi dam chos skyong gis gzhung bsrang la mchod bstod bsnyen pa yan chad bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:304: spyi don bzhi pa tshogs gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:306: gnyis gang rung gis gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:307: bla ma dang dal gyi gtso bo dbyer med pa'i
NK016(ma)002:308: thugs ka nas h'u dkar ser dmar ljang bzhi spros
NK016(ma)002:309: / sgo bzhir gsang ba'i lha mo bzhir gyur pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:310: shar du rgyas 'debs ma dkar mo /
NK016(ma)002:311: lhor dam pa ma ser mo /
NK016(ma)002:312: nub tu zab mo dmar po /
NK016(ma)002:313: byang du tshe 'phel ma ljang ku /
NK016(ma)002:314: lha mo de rnams kyi thugs kar thal mo sbyar
NK016(ma)002:315: nas gsol ba gdab pa'i sngon du man+dala 'bul dgos
NK016(ma)002:317: zhu ba po gcig las med na /
NK016(ma)002:318: dmigs pa lha mo bzhir bsgom dgos /
NK016(ma)002:319: slob ma mi 'dug nas rang gcig pu yin na yang /
NK016(ma)002:320: cho ga chad ma nyan pa'i don la /
NK016(ma)002:322: dmigs pa gong bzhin du byed /
NK016(ma)002:326: gsang sngags gnyis med kyis don rtogs pa'i rdo rje
NK016(ma)002:327: slob dpona bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis phun sum tshogs
NK016(ma)002:328: pa'i dapala dang ldan pa khyod la zhu ba ni
NK016(ma)002:329: / srid pa'i sdug bsngal ste khams gsum 'khor ba'i
NK016(ma)002:330: sdug bsngal rgyud nga 'bras bu rtsa ba nas bacada
NK016(ma)002:331: / pa'i phyir dang / byis pa'i ces pa che la ltos na /
NK016(ma)002:336: so so skye bo byis pa /
NK016(ma)002:339: 'dir ni gsang sngags la ltos na mtshan nyid byis pa'i lam 'dod yon lnga po spang ba yin /
NK016(ma)002:341: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i spyod pa'i khyad para
NK016(ma)002:342: gyis chos 'dod yon lnga po spang ba med par
NK016(ma)002:343: lam du khyer bar madzada du gsola /
NK016(ma)002:346: dusa 'das ma 'ongs da lta bslad nas byon pa dang bzhi /
NK016(ma)002:347: zhing khams bsam yasa kyis snang stong gnyis med kyis gnas lugs la bde bar ste /
NK016(ma)002:348: de nar son pa la gshegsa pa ste sangs rgyas
NK016(ma)002:349: thamsa cada dang de'i sras kyis tshogas rig 'dzin dang
NK016(ma)002:350: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad 'dus shing khams ji
NK016(ma)002:351: snyed pa rnams ni gsang sngags thun mong ma yin
NK016(ma)002:352: pa'i spyod pa'i khyad para 'dod yon lnga po 'di
NK016(ma)002:353: mi spang zhing lam du khyer ba lasa byung /
NK016(ma)002:354: gtan tshig de basa na 'dod yon lnga po spang
NK016(ma)002:355: mi dgos par bde ba chena po de yisa don
NK016(ma)002:356: nyams su len pa la ngo matshara don rmad du
NK016(ma)002:357: byung ba la yanga dag de lta bu'i don rdo
NK016(ma)002:358: rje slob dpon khyed kyis gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs
NK016(ma)002:359: pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo rnams la bstan du gsola
NK016(ma)002:360: / byang ba stong pa'i rang bzhin /
NK016(ma)002:361: chub pa snang ba'i rang bzhin /
NK016(ma)002:362: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i don la byang chub
NK016(ma)002:363: snying po mchoga don la sangs rgyas ma thob kyis
NK016(ma)002:364: bar du 'dod yon spang ba med par lam du
NK016(ma)002:365: khyer bas na bdee mchoga spyod pa ces zer ro
NK016(ma)002:366: // gsang sngags kyis don 'di lta bu la ma
NK016(ma)002:367: dad pa'i the tshom za ba lta bu ma yin
NK016(ma)002:368: par nyams su len pa la yang dag blang ces
NK016(ma)002:369: tshig rkang gnyis po 'di ni 'khor rnal 'byor pho
NK016(ma)002:370: mo rnams kyi 'dod yon la spyod par khas len
NK016(ma)002:371: // pa'o // de ltar lan gsum gsol ba gdab bo //
NK016(ma)002:372: de'i don ni dang po ngag 'khyal /
NK016(ma)002:374: gal che na lan gsum gsol ba gdab bo //
NK016(ma)002:375: skabs 'dir lha mo bzhi thugs ka na tshur bsdu gsung yang /
NK016(ma)002:376: da rung 'og ma zhu len dgos pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:377: tshogs ma tshar gyi bar du mi bsdu'o //
NK016(ma)002:378: de nas rdo rje slob dpon nas bzung ste kun gyis tshogs byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:379: sngar sman byin rlabs byas zin de skyog gang bcus
NK016(ma)002:380: la tshogs chang nang du bsre la phud phar la
NK016(ma)002:381: blug / de nas thig gcig thabs rdzas kyi steng du blug /
NK016(ma)002:382: bsang chu byin rlabs byas nas /
NK016(ma)002:386: gtor ma'i steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo /
NK016(ma)002:388: smad dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i mchod pa /
NK016(ma)002:389: sman byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs pa ni gzhung bzhin du bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:390: de nas tshogs zhing spyan drangs pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:391: dpung pa g.yas g.yon gnyis na byang chub kyi rtsa gnyis yod par bshad pa'i don la /
NK016(ma)002:392: lag bsnol nas dpung pa gnyis kyi thad kar se gol gtogs la /
NK016(ma)002:393: badz+ra sa ma na dza h'u dza /
NK016(ma)002:395: de'i don badz+ra ni snang stod gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams so //
NK016(ma)002:396: sa mana dza h'u dza ni dam tshig la dgongs nas 'dir gshegs shig /
NK016(ma)002:399: lag ngar dang ni rdo rje bcings //
NK016(ma)002:400: lag pa g.yas dang g.yon pa ni //
NK016(ma)002:401: se gol mnyam par gtogs pa yis //
NK016(ma)002:402: sangs rgyas thams cad byon par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)002:404: mdun gyi nam mkhar tshogs zhing la phur pa lta bu yin na /
NK016(ma)002:405: g.yas su zhi ba'i lha tshogs /
NK016(ma)002:406: g.yon du khro bo'i lha tshogs /
NK016(ma)002:407: steng gi cha la slob dpon pad+ma la sogs rig
NK016(ma)002:408: 'dzin brgyud pa'i bla ma dang 'og gi cha la
NK016(ma)002:409: chos skyong ma mgon la sogs bka' sdod bstan bsrung
NK016(ma)002:410: rnams dang / g.yas su pha brgyud kyi lha tshogs /
NK016(ma)002:411: g.yon du ma rgyud kyi lha tshogs /
NK016(ma)002:412: mdun du gnyis med kyi lha tshogs rnams bsgom par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:413: bka' gsar rnying gi gang zag phyogs 'dzin can 'ga'
NK016(ma)002:414: zhig gis rang rang gi yi dam lha bsgom nas
NK016(ma)002:415: gzhan gyi lha bsgom pa bslad ma yin skad /
NK016(ma)002:416: chos spangs gi las bsags pa mang po mthong ngo //
NK016(ma)002:417: chos spang gi las bsags na nyes pa ni dran
NK016(ma)002:418: pa nyer bzhag nang nas lce dpag tshad lnga brgya'i
NK016(ma)002:420: lcags kyi thong so me 'bar ba lnga brgyas rmo gsungs so //
NK016(ma)002:421: de nas tshogs gzi byin bskyed pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:422: rdo rje dril bu 'dzin la dbyangs dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK016(ma)002:423: h'u cha lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bo yin pas /
NK016(ma)002:425: dper na 'byung ba chena po nama mkha'a 'di ni /
NK016(ma)002:426: sa chu me rlung 'byung ba chena po bzhin nam mkha' las 'byung ba'am /
NK016(ma)002:427: ma g.yos pas nam mkha' dang lnga pa ste /
NK016(ma)002:428: nam mkha'a la ni skye 'gro phyi nang gi chos 'doda pa thams cad 'byung ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:429: don ni phyi nang gi mchod rdzas zad mi shes
NK016(ma)002:430: pa'i don 'doda pa'i mchod pa 'grub para shog ces
NK016(ma)002:431: mchod rdzas la smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:432: tshogs zhing la smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:433: 'doda pa'i mchod pasa mnyes gyur ciga /
NK016(ma)002:434: +amo cha lnga ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am ye shes lnga'i ngo bo'o //
NK016(ma)002:435: na masarba ta th+aa ga ta pu tsa badz+ra swa
NK016(ma)002:436: b+h+aa wa ne stong pa +aat+ma ko& ham ni bdag
NK016(ma)002:437: nyid yin no // de nas kun bzang mchod 'bul la bzhi ste /
NK016(ma)002:441: de kho na nyid kyi mchod pa dang bzhi'o //
NK016(ma)002:442: de la kun tu bzang po phyi'i mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:443: 'jig rten khams kyi rgya mtsho thams cad ni yon chab /
NK016(ma)002:444: lho sprin dang na bun thams cad ni bdug spos /
NK016(ma)002:445: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad ni me tog /
NK016(ma)002:446: nyi zla gza' skar thams cad ni snang gsal /
NK016(ma)002:447: chu bo thams cad ni byugs pa /
NK016(ma)002:448: ri bo thams cad ni zhal zas /
NK016(ma)002:449: sgra grags thams cad ni rol mor byin gyis brlabs
NK016(ma)002:450: nas 'bul dgos par bshad 'di la snang grags mchod
NK016(ma)002:452: kun tu ngan pa'i mtshan nyid med pas kun bzang mchod pa ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:453: kun tu bzang po nang gi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:454: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyan sngar gzugs thams cad sdug pa /
NK016(ma)002:459: tshogs drug gi snang ba thams cad 'dod yon gyi mchod par gyur pas /
NK016(ma)002:460: kun tu ngan pa'i mtshan nyid med pas na kun bzang mchod pa ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:464: dran rtog thugs kyi khyer so dang gsum la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:465: de kho na nyid kyis mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:466: ma skyes mi 'gags dbyer med la bya ste /
NK016(ma)002:467: skye med kyi gnas lugs gdangs 'gag pa med pa mchod pa'i tshogs su shar /
NK016(ma)002:468: shar ba'i dus de nyid na skye med kyi gnas lugs rang la ma g.yos pas dbyer med pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:469: dper na rgya mtsho dang gzugs brnyan bzhin no //
NK016(ma)002:470: don la 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi bsdus pa'i chos
NK016(ma)002:471: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i mchod par ma gyur
NK016(ma)002:473: bde bar gshegas ces pa gnas lugs zab mo'i don rtogs shing nar son pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:474: de lta bu'i bde bar gshegs pa yin so cog
NK016(ma)002:475: rnams ni sangs rgyas bcoma ldan 'das rnams yin no
NK016(ma)002:476: // bdud bzhi bcom pas na bcom /
NK016(ma)002:477: che ba'i yon tan dang ldan pas snang stong rtag
NK016(ma)002:478: chad kyi mtha' las 'das pa ces pa'i don no
NK016(ma)002:479: // mtha' gnyis dang bdud bzhi las rgyal ba grangs mang ba'am /
NK016(ma)002:480: rgya che bas rgya mtsho lta bu'i gzugs skur bzhengs
NK016(ma)002:481: pa de yang gzugs sku rang kha ma yin gyi
NK016(ma)002:482: nang dgongs pa ye shes kyi rang gzugs phyi rol
NK016(ma)002:483: du rgyal ba'i skur shar ba ni snang ba sku
NK016(ma)002:484: dang ye shes su shar ba ni kun bzang gis
NK016(ma)002:485: mchod pa'o // srid pa khams gsum 'khor ba'i 'gro
NK016(ma)002:486: ba rigs drug gi sems can rgya mtsho mtha'a yasa
NK016(ma)002:487: pa'i sems can rnams kyi spyod pa ci ltar snang
NK016(ma)002:488: mchod pa'o // yang / snang ba sku /
NK016(ma)002:490: dran rig thugs su khyer ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:491: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa /
NK016(ma)002:492: lam theg pa mtho dman nam zag bcas zag med
NK016(ma)002:493: kyi spyod pa rgya mtsho de rnams la skyon med
NK016(ma)002:494: pas na rmada byung yang dag pa kun sems kyi
NK016(ma)002:495: gnas lugs rig rtsal 'gag med du shar ba kun
NK016(ma)002:497: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK016(ma)002:498: phyi nang gsang gsum de kho na nyid dang bzhi'i
NK016(ma)002:499: mchod pa las ma g.yos pas na kun bazanga mchoda
NK016(ma)002:500: pa zhes bya'o // sprin ni dper na zad pa med par thams cad 'byung ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:501: mchoga tu rola pa ni kun bzang mchod pa mchod pa'i tshogs yin la /
NK016(ma)002:502: rol ba ni gdul bya'i ngo la mchod pa de
NK016(ma)002:503: tshogs zhing gis len cing bzhes su gsol ba ni
NK016(ma)002:504: rol ba'o // ni sngags kyi mgo 'dren cing ye shes lnga'i ngo bo'o //
NK016(ma)002:505: na mahni phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod pa zhes bya ba la sogs don bcu tsam la 'jug na'ang /
NK016(ma)002:507: gang la na sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:508: b+hi shwa mu khe b+h+ya sna tshogs pa'i gdong pa can mchod mgron rnams so //
NK016(ma)002:509: sarba thams cad tad khanga nam mkha' ut+ga te ni
NK016(ma)002:510: gnas pa s+pha ra na ni 'gro ba'am khyab pa'i
NK016(ma)002:511: mchod pa'o // des ci tsam khyab snyam na hi
NK016(ma)002:512: mam ga ga na kham 'di'i nam mkha'i khams gang
NK016(ma)002:513: ba'i s+w+aa h+aa ni gyur pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:514: rmad byung gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:515: thog mar gtor ma'i steng gi khams drug gi lha mos mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:516: gzugs kyi lha mo dkar mos phyag na me long bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)002:517: sgra'i lha mo sngon mos phyag na pi wam 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)002:518: dri'i lha mo ser mos phyag na spos bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)002:519: ro'i lha mo dmar mos phyag na zhal zas ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)002:520: reg bya'i lha mo ljang gu phyag na na bza' gong ba rdo rjes mtshan pa bsnams pa /
NK016(ma)002:521: chos kyi lha mo mthing kas phyag na e gru gsum bsnams pa rnams kyis /
NK016(ma)002:522: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi spyan dang /
NK016(ma)002:526: thugs kar thim par bsgom la /
NK016(ma)002:527: tshig gis don ni h'u ni glu'i mgo 'dren pa yin la /
NK016(ma)002:528: gzugsa kyi lha mo dkar mos ni lag pa gnyis
NK016(ma)002:529: kyis me longa gnyis s+t+wa zur gnyis su 'dzina cing
NK016(ma)002:530: / gzugsa shin tu mdzesa pa'i lha mos lag pa gar spyod pasa phyogsa bcur g.yosa nas /
NK016(ma)002:531: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid dang ldan zhing 'od
NK016(ma)002:532: 'abra ba'i gzugsa kyi lha mo de bzhin gshegs pa
NK016(ma)002:533: thams cad kyi spyan la thima par bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:534: badz+ra r+au pa h'u ni gzugs rdo rje ma ces pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:535: lha mo bzhi ni go sla'o //
NK016(ma)002:536: sngags kyi sgra rdo rje ma'o //
NK016(ma)002:540: chos kyi lha mo ni blo'i yul du gyur tshad kyi chos thams cad bsdu na /
NK016(ma)002:541: 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas gnyis la 'du /
NK016(ma)002:544: 'gog pa la so sor brtags pa'i 'gogs pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:545: so sor brtags min gyis 'gog pa gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:546: de rnams gnas su dag pa'am /
NK016(ma)002:547: snang stong gnyis med kyi don ngo bo 'gyur ba med pas na rdo rje /
NK016(ma)002:548: stong la thams cad 'byung ba ni nam mkha' /
NK016(ma)002:549: chos kyi lha mo sku chos nyid 'gyur ba med
NK016(ma)002:550: pas na sku mdog mthing ka phyag mtshan chos 'byung
NK016(ma)002:551: bsnams pa / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK016(ma)002:552: thugs kyi dgongs pa dang gnyis su med pa'i don
NK016(ma)002:553: bsnams pa / la / rtags la chos kyi lha
NK016(ma)002:554: mo de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kar
NK016(ma)002:556: d+harma d+hartu ni chos thams cad badz+ra rdo rje swa
NK016(ma)002:557: b+h+aa wa stong pa rnam par dag pa +aat+ma ko&
NK016(ma)002:558: ham ni bdag nyid yin no //
NK016(ma)002:559: des khams drug gi lha mo'i mchod pa song nas /
NK016(ma)002:560: gtor ma bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur par bsgom la /
NK016(ma)002:561: lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gur gyur nas
NK016(ma)002:562: chu la nyi zer phog pa bzhin du gsol bar
NK016(ma)002:563: bsam mo // 'di yan chad kyi mchod pa ni zhi khro thun mong gi mchod pa yin no //
NK016(ma)002:564: gtor ma'i 'og dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i mchod
NK016(ma)002:565: pa ni khyad par du khro bo'i lha tshogs la
NK016(ma)002:567: de yang kahthoga pa'i phyag len la /
NK016(ma)002:569: g.yas pas rdo rje bsor zhing zhags bsdog byed /
NK016(ma)002:573: lha cha thams cad 'ur gyis bsgrags so //
NK016(ma)002:574: drag po'i phrin las kyi skabs yin pas so //
NK016(ma)002:575: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i bsgral ba'i zhing chena ni bam skye ba bdun pa yin te /
NK016(ma)002:576: de'i dri ni ngada dpunga dpung zer ba yin /
NK016(ma)002:577: bam 'di dngos su yod na ma dang mkha' 'gro sprin bzhin 'du /
NK016(ma)002:578: so so'i skye bo tha mal ba yin na bam
NK016(ma)002:579: 'di'i sha zos dri tshor na ngan song rdog pas
NK016(ma)002:580: non par gsang sngags kyis rgyud gzhung nas gsungs so
NK016(ma)002:581: // 'dir ni dngos su ma yin yang ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:582: 'dod chags ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su
NK016(ma)002:583: rak+ta rgya mtsho'i rba rlabas kyi li li ni lha
NK016(ma)002:584: tshogs thams cad kyis gsol bar bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:585: zhe sdang ma spang gnas su dag pa'i rtags su
NK016(ma)002:586: kem rus manga po'i tshogas ni khra la la byed
NK016(ma)002:587: pa rus pa'i gram khrod lha tshogs rnams kyis gsol
NK016(ma)002:588: bar bsgom mo // gti mug ma spangs gnas su
NK016(ma)002:589: dag pa'i rtags su mam sa gala chena tshogas ni
NK016(ma)002:590: thanga mar bdal ba ni sha'i ri bo rnams lha
NK016(ma)002:591: tshogs thams cad kyis bza' bar bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:592: 'di ltar dug gsum mchoda pa gsang sngags rdo rje
NK016(ma)002:593: theg pa'i lugs kyis gtsang tsog med pa'am nyon mongs
NK016(ma)002:594: pa dug gsum spang ba med par lam du khyer
NK016(ma)002:595: ba'i don gyis na sha khrag rus gsum gyi mchod
NK016(ma)002:596: pa bshamsa pa lagas mod kyis /
NK016(ma)002:597: 'di 'bul ba'i zhing ni nyon mongs pa tshang tshing
NK016(ma)002:598: dad 'dra ba thams cad bsreg cing gdug pa can
NK016(ma)002:600: rtags bskal ba mara 'grib zad pa'i dus mtha'i me
NK016(ma)002:601: ltar 'abra ba'i klong dkyil nasa sku bzhengs pa lta
NK016(ma)002:602: bu'o // bdud ru tra la sogs pa drag byed thams cad 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK016(ma)002:603: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen por snang ngo //
NK016(ma)002:604: bcom ldan ni gsang sngags kyis bshad lugs gzhan dang mthun la /
NK016(ma)002:605: dapala ni dpal gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:606: chena po ni gong na med pa'i don no //
NK016(ma)002:607: 'dod chags ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su g.yon gyi dung dmar zhal du stob pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:609: he dgyes pa 'di la bdag tu dgyes pa dang gzhan du dgyes pa gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:611: bdag don du chags pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:612: gzhan don du chags pa gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:613: ka ka ra na mdzad pa yin te /
NK016(ma)002:615: dpal gsum nyid ldan dgyes pa rnam gnyis kyis /
NK016(ma)002:616: chags ga nyis mi gtong 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK016(ma)002:617: ces he ru ka'i bshad pa la de ltar du gsungs so //
NK016(ma)002:618: khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor 'di ni sangsa rgyas
NK016(ma)002:619: kyi zhing yin la nyon mongas sgrol ba'i madzada pa'i
NK016(ma)002:620: rtags su sha rus khrag gsum bza' /
NK016(ma)002:621: mchod pa 'di rnams ni 'gro ba'i dona la dper na /
NK016(ma)002:622: yida bzhina gyi nor bu che la gsol ba btab
NK016(ma)002:623: na dgos 'dod 'byung ba bzhin du mchod pa'i tshogs
NK016(ma)002:624: mi 'dra ba sna tshogs su shar ba 'di rnams
NK016(ma)002:626: yang na 'gro ba'i don la yid bzhin gyi nor
NK016(ma)002:627: bu rin po che la dgos 'dod 'byung ba bzhin
NK016(ma)002:628: du / gang la gang 'dul de la dera skur
NK016(ma)002:629: ston pa'i ched du bde bar rol ste mchod pa
NK016(ma)002:630: 'di rnams bzhes su gsol ces byas na rung /
NK016(ma)002:631: tshogsa rje ces pa ni tshogs kyi rje bo la bos pa lta bu /
NK016(ma)002:632: rngam pa'i mchoda pa ni dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i mchod pa 'di bzhesa su gsola /
NK016(ma)002:633: kenga rus tshogsa la sogs pa'i mchod pa /
NK016(ma)002:634: de rnams tshogs zhing rnams kyi bstod pa'i tshul du
NK016(ma)002:635: ston par byed cinga khyad par du loga 'drena gdug
NK016(ma)002:636: pa'i bduda dpung 'jomas par madzada pa'i /
NK016(ma)002:637: phyi'i mkha' 'gro dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:639: yul sum cu so gnyis la gnas pa'i rang rgyud pa rnams dang /
NK016(ma)002:640: nang gi mkha' 'gro de rnams 'dul bar byed pa'i sprul pa rnams dang /
NK016(ma)002:641: de lta bu'i phyi nang gi mkha' 'gro ma manga po'i tshogas dang bacasa pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:642: gzhan yang gduga pa'i stobsa chena ces pa ni chos skyong ma mgon mgar gsum /
NK016(ma)002:643: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:644: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:646: dregs pa nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK016(ma)002:647: bswe lcags dung gsum gyi tshogs dang /
NK016(ma)002:651: pho nya manga po'i tshogas ces pa ni pho nya drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK016(ma)002:653: de lta bu'i las mkhan pho nya dang bcas pa la /
NK016(ma)002:655: zhe sdang rus pa'i phung po /
NK016(ma)002:656: gti mug sha'i ri bo de lta bu'i /
NK016(ma)002:657: dug gsum rgya mtsho'i mchod pa bzhesa su gsol /
NK016(ma)002:660: sarba ta th+aa ga ta +aa wa lo ki te
NK016(ma)002:661: a mri ta h'u kha ram kha ram ta ki
NK016(ma)002:662: ni yo ni dang s+t+wam b+ha ga te a la
NK016(ma)002:663: la ho / dgra bgegs gdug pa can gyi ma h+aa mam sa la kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)002:664: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)002:665: ma h+aa tsit+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)002:666: ma h+aa ba su ta la kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)002:667: skye mched bcu gnyis la kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)002:668: rnam shes tshogs brgyad la kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)002:669: spyi don lnga pa mchod cing rol pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:670: gong gi lha mo bzhi'i zhu ba byed par bsgom la /
NK016(ma)002:671: phyag tshang pas tshogs rdzas bteg la 'di skad brjod do //
NK016(ma)002:672: tshogs rdzas 'di la rnam rtog mi rung bzhi zhu ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:673: kye gzigas shiga ces pa ni tshogs kyi gtso bo la bos pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:674: 'dod yon spang ba med par lam du khyer ba la /
NK016(ma)002:675: mdzesa ldan dam pa'i chos yin /
NK016(ma)002:676: 'di la bzang ngan dang gtsang rtsog gi rnam rtog
NK016(ma)002:677: byed mi rung dper na bram ze gtsang ma dang
NK016(ma)002:678: / khyi dang gdol pa gnyis rtsog pa yin te 'di gsuma /
NK016(ma)002:679: ranga bzhina gciga pa nyid du rol ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:680: de ci yi phyir zhe na /
NK016(ma)002:681: gzung 'dzin gnyis kyi nang nas rag pa gtsang sme gnyis yin /
NK016(ma)002:682: gtsang sme gnyis kyi rtog pa sbyang bar byed pa la bdud rtsi lnga nyams su len dgos /
NK016(ma)002:683: 'di la mos pa nyams su len pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:684: nus pa nyams su len pa gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:685: mos pa nyams su len pa la ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams len dang /
NK016(ma)002:687: de gnyis ni las dang po ba'i spyod yul yin /
NK016(ma)002:688: nus pa lam du khyer ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:689: phyag rgya spros pa mthar phyin nas sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga thug 'phrad du nyams su len /
NK016(ma)002:692: lug sha gsum la khyad med /
NK016(ma)002:693: chang dang dri chu gnyis la khyad med par nyams su len thub dgos /
NK016(ma)002:694: rjes shes la gtsang rtsog shar yang tshom bu tshogs bsgrub bas sbyangs dgos /
NK016(ma)002:695: zag med tshe rnam gnyis kyi skabs su phyin pa'i
NK016(ma)002:696: dus su mnyam rjes med par gtsang rtsog 'dzin pa
NK016(ma)002:698: nyon yid gtan ldog red pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)002:699: nus pa lam du khyer ba'i skabs su rgya gar ba rnams kyi bdud rtsi lnga rang dang /
NK016(ma)002:702: khyad par du mdze sha tshogs la bsham par snang /
NK016(ma)002:703: gnyis pa tshogs la rol bar zhu ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:705: gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin gyi tshogs kyi gtso bo
NK016(ma)002:706: sogas kyi sgras rnal 'byor pho mo rnams dang bcas
NK016(ma)002:709: gsan par zhu bas zhal gyis phyogs /
NK016(ma)002:711: spyan gyis gzigs su gsol byas na'ang rung ngo //
NK016(ma)002:712: tshig rkang gsum po ni go sla'o //
NK016(ma)002:713: gong gi bram ze nes pa'i skabs la gtam rgyud 'di ltar du gsungs /
NK016(ma)002:714: sngon rgya gar gyi yul na rdol bya ba dang /
NK016(ma)002:715: bram ze khyo shug gnyis yod skad /
NK016(ma)002:716: khong gi khang pa de lding khang gnyis yod skad /
NK016(ma)002:717: der bram ze steng khang du bsdad nas chung mas 'og khang du 'bras thugs btsos /
NK016(ma)002:718: de 'khar gzhong du khyer 'ong nas gang bram ze la 'dren /
NK016(ma)002:719: gang mo rang gi za ba yin pa las /
NK016(ma)002:720: gang mang ba gcig bram ze de za skyen par
NK016(ma)002:721: byung bas chung mas kho ma 'grangs par tshor nas
NK016(ma)002:722: da rung khyer nas 'ong ngam byas pas khyer rung
NK016(ma)002:723: zer skad / lar bram ze bya ba des zas zos pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:724: cho ga mang po bya dgos pa yod do //
NK016(ma)002:725: de nam dga' dgar bza' bar med /
NK016(ma)002:727: der 'og khang du song ba dang /
NK016(ma)002:728: yun thag ring gcig lon pas /
NK016(ma)002:729: bram ze de ngang thung nas bltas pas /
NK016(ma)002:730: mos 'bras thugs khyer nas byung bram ze la drangs bas /
NK016(ma)002:731: bram ze mo'i zhabs khrag thig gcig 'dug pa mthong ste /
NK016(ma)002:732: khos na re khyod kyi khrag de mngal khrag yin te 'ong bas mi 'dod zer /
NK016(ma)002:733: der mos na re 'di mngal khrag min /
NK016(ma)002:734: nga la lo rgyus yod zo dang byas pas /
NK016(ma)002:735: der khos 'grangs par zos te lo rgyus shod byas pas /
NK016(ma)002:736: mos na red mkha' 'gro ma yin /
NK016(ma)002:737: da kyi yul pa la pu tra bya bar rgyal po bsad pas /
NK016(ma)002:738: ngas de'i ro khyer nas 'ong ste d+hi wi kro tra bya bar bskyal nas yod /
NK016(ma)002:739: do nub mkha' 'gro ma thams cad d+he wi ko tra ra 'tshogs nas tshogs kyi 'khor lo byed /
NK016(ma)002:740: nga yang der 'gro dgos pas khyod dang de ring bas 'grog yun med skad /
NK016(ma)002:741: de nas rdol nas pa la pu trar 'gro ba
NK016(ma)002:742: la mi gsha' ma 'gro ba'i lam la zla ba
NK016(ma)002:743: phyed yod / pa la pu tra nas d+he wi
NK016(ma)002:744: ba ko trar 'gro ba la zla ba phyed yod
NK016(ma)002:745: phyed yod / / d+he wi ko tra nas rdol du 'gro ba la zla ba phyed yod skad /
NK016(ma)002:746: mos zla ba phyed gnyis kyi lam dal gcig la 'khor nas byung skad /
NK016(ma)002:747: der bram ze mo la nga'ang khrid par zhu byas pas /
NK016(ma)002:748: mos na re khyod bram ze bya ba shin tu
NK016(ma)002:749: rnam rtog che bas gsang sngags kyi snod ma yin
NK016(ma)002:751: bram ze mo 'o skol gnyis de tsam gcig 'grogs
NK016(ma)002:752: 'grogs nas dang mi khrid dam rnam rtog mi byed
NK016(ma)002:753: byas pas / pha ki der khrid par khas blang
NK016(ma)002:754: pas do nub sa sros tsam na mo'i rdzu 'phrul
NK016(ma)002:756: ci tsug yin cha med par d+he wi ko trar phyin pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:757: de na mkha' 'gro ma mang pa la las mi ro mang po khyer nas byung /
NK016(ma)002:758: la las rta ro mang po khyer nas byang /
NK016(ma)002:760: la las spos kyi bye brag /
NK016(ma)002:762: la las dri'i bye brag mang po khyer nas byung skad /
NK016(ma)002:763: der mkha' 'gro thams cad 'dus pa dang mi ro gcig gis thod pa bkog ste /
NK016(ma)002:764: thod pa sha bkra ba gcig gis chang lhub kyis
NK016(ma)002:765: bcus nas mkha' 'gro ma thams cad kyis hub bskor
NK016(ma)002:766: byas te bram ze la drangs pas /
NK016(ma)002:767: bram ze thod pa'i phyogs su yang mi bsnyen /
NK016(ma)002:768: chang gis phyogs su yang mi bsnyen pa yin pas /
NK016(ma)002:769: khos sna bkab pas ma 'dod skad /
NK016(ma)002:770: der mkha' 'gro ma thams cad kyis brkyangs nas hub gcig 'thung byas pas /
NK016(ma)002:771: khyad par du kho rang gi chung mas 'di la hub gcig 'thung byas pas kyang ma btub bo //
NK016(ma)002:772: der mkha' 'gro ma gcig gis kho rang gi spar ba zed du bcug /
NK016(ma)002:773: der me tog phul rang gi phyag gis bkab kho
NK016(ma)002:774: la mig btsum gcig gsung nas der khos mig btsum
NK016(ma)002:775: pas / de te zhag bdun na 'dir shog zer tsam na /
NK016(ma)002:776: ci ltar yin cha med par kho rang khyim gyi mal sa rnyid par phyin nas 'dug ste /
NK016(ma)002:777: der kho na nas zhag bdun nas shi skad /
NK016(ma)002:778: da lta'i chang de la hub gcig 'thung na de
NK016(ma)002:779: nyid du phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub
NK016(ma)002:781: de'i phyir mkha' 'gro ma'i ci gsung nyan dgos skad /
NK016(ma)002:783: rdo rje slob dpon gyis lan btab pa la gsum ste /
NK016(ma)002:784: tshogs gnyis 'dod don lam gyi don la mnyes pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:785: tshogs kyi rang bzhin sku gsum du bstan pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:786: de'i rgyu yo byad lam du khyer ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:788: rang byung ye shes chena po lasa byung ba'i 'bras
NK016(ma)002:789: bu ye shes kyi tshogas chena 'abra ba'i don gyis
NK016(ma)002:790: na nyon mongas pa rang rgyud bsrega go //
NK016(ma)002:791: 'dod yon spangs pa med par 'di 'dra'i bde ba thoba nas ni /
NK016(ma)002:792: rnal 'byor pho mo kun gyis a ho ma h+aa su kha brjod dgos so //
NK016(ma)002:793: a la la ni ngo mtshar /
NK016(ma)002:798: gnyis pa tshogs kyi rang bzhin sku gsum du bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK016(ma)002:799: dang po tshogs kyi dal sku gsum du ngo sprad pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:800: 'dod yon lnga la ci ltar spyod na yang stong
NK016(ma)002:801: pa nyid la blo 'byor dgos pasa de'i rtagsa su
NK016(ma)002:802: dam pa rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas
NK016(ma)002:803: 'byung / sangs rgyas de'i dbye ba la bde mchoga ni chos sku /
NK016(ma)002:805: bde bar madzada pa'i ni longs sku'o //
NK016(ma)002:806: sku gsum dbyer med pa'i don ni /
NK016(ma)002:807: riga pa'i skyes bu rdo rje semsa dapa'a yin ste
NK016(ma)002:808: gsang sngags kyi tshogs gnyis 'di la longs spyod na
NK016(ma)002:809: rdo rje'i sems dpa'i go 'phang thob bo //
NK016(ma)002:810: gnyis pa byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:811: rdo rje sems dpa' de thob pa'i rgyu ni rtsa
NK016(ma)002:812: ba byang ba stong pa'i rang bzhin yi ge 'dod
NK016(ma)002:813: yon lang ci ltar snang yang rang rgyud du ma
NK016(ma)002:815: chub pa snang ba'i rang bzhin yin te 'dod yon lnga 'gags med du shar zhing snang bas /
NK016(ma)002:816: semsa rig pa'i rang bzhin snang stong gnyis su med
NK016(ma)002:817: pa don rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis riga pasa riga
NK016(ma)002:818: pa ni gnad shin tu che'o //
NK016(ma)002:819: byang chub semsa rig na ni dngosa grub kyis mchog sangs rgyas thob pa yin no //
NK016(ma)002:820: de lta bu'i don riga na mi bslu mi 'gyur ba'i yang dag nyid ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:821: 'od dang mngona shes mnga' la sogas pa ldan yanga gnoda sbyin chosa mi shisa ces pa'i don ni /
NK016(ma)002:822: byang chub sems ma rtogs par lus la 'od byung ba dang /
NK016(ma)002:823: zag bcas kyi mngon shes mnga' ba dang /
NK016(ma)002:824: brag la thog pa med pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:825: chu la mi bying ba dang /
NK016(ma)002:826: de la sogs pa'i rdzu 'phrul ni 'jig rten gyi lha klu gnod sbyin mthu bo che dang /
NK016(ma)002:827: bdud dang mu stegs can la'ang yod de /
NK016(ma)002:828: de dag ni sangs rgyas kyi dngos grub ga la thob ste /
NK016(ma)002:829: chos nyid zab mo'i don ma rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)002:830: de bas byang chub sems rtogs na thun mong gi dngos grub ma byung yang /
NK016(ma)002:831: mchog gis dngos grub 'di yin no //
NK016(ma)002:832: gong gi mngon shes mnga' ba zhes bya ba 'di
NK016(ma)002:833: la yig cha 'ga' zhig la grangs kyis lnga zer
NK016(ma)002:834: ba snang ste / yi ge mi dag pa e yin snyam mo //
NK016(ma)002:835: zag bcas zag med kyis mngon shes lnga ka shes na /
NK016(ma)002:836: ldan yang gnod sbyin mi shes zer ba dang 'gal lo //
NK016(ma)002:837: bka' bstan chos kyis gzhung lugs dang bstun na /
NK016(ma)002:838: de yang lha'i rna ba dang mig gi mngon shes gnyis ni /
NK016(ma)002:839: rna ba dang mig gis mngon shes khyad par can
NK016(ma)002:840: dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin la
NK016(ma)002:841: / lhag ma bzhin ye shes dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin no //
NK016(ma)002:843: gsum pa yo byad lam du khyer nas 'dod yon tshogs su bstan pa la gsum las /
NK016(ma)002:844: dang po bgo ba dang bza' ba'i yo byad ni /
NK016(ma)002:845: stong nyid zab mo'i don rnal ma la rang rig pa'i blo 'byor bas na rnala 'byor ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:849: sar smin pa dang gsum mo //
NK016(ma)002:850: 'dir ni zag bcas gsang sngags kyis sor chud pa'i riga 'dzina can no //
NK016(ma)002:851: dama ldan pasa ces pa ni rdo rje'i ming sring lcam dral la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:852: na baza'a dang ni ces pa la zhi chas dang /
NK016(ma)002:854: zhi ba la sku'i stod g.yog dang /
NK016(ma)002:860: kun la khyab pa'i chos gos la sogs pa'i rgyan dang bdun no //
NK016(ma)002:861: khro bo la glang chen gyi ko rlon dang /
NK016(ma)002:864: thod pa'i phreng ba rnams so //
NK016(ma)002:865: rgya gar gyi tshogs nang na 'di rnams dngos su byed pa mthong ngo //
NK016(ma)002:866: 'dir ni ting nge 'dzin tsam yin no //
NK016(ma)002:867: zhal zas rnams ces pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:875: zan la sogs pa bza' ba'i bye brag rnams dang /
NK016(ma)002:882: sbrang chu la sogs pa'i btung ba'i bye brag rnams so //
NK016(ma)002:883: bsgrub pa'i rdzas su dabnga bskur ste ces pa ni bgo ba dang bza' btung de rnams la /
NK016(ma)002:886: dbyer med pa byang chub sems su rtogs na grub pa'i rdzas su dbang bskur ba'am /
NK016(ma)002:888: de lta bu'i sgo nas na bza' dang bza' ba
NK016(ma)002:889: rnams gsola na dngosa grub mchoga ste 'bras bu sangs
NK016(ma)002:891: gnyis pa glu tshig sgra'i yo byad ni /
NK016(ma)002:892: tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi skabs la /
NK016(ma)002:893: glu'i bye brag rigs lnga'i glu len lugs yod kyang /
NK016(ma)002:895: 'dir glu ni dbyangs rta la mkhas pa dang tshigs
NK016(ma)002:896: ni tshigs su bcad pa du ma rnams dang ldan
NK016(ma)002:897: pa / de dag gis sgra rnams ni sgra de
NK016(ma)002:898: dag ma 'gag mi dmigs dbyer med pa byang chub
NK016(ma)002:900: sgra grags stong dbyer med pa de bzhin gshegs pa
NK016(ma)002:901: rnams kyi gsunga gi ngo bora byin gyis brlabs pa
NK016(ma)002:902: ste / grags stong dbyer med kyi ngang nas bsgrag
NK016(ma)002:903: na dngosa grub kyis ma choga sangs rgyas thob par
NK016(ma)002:905: rol mo'i sgra skad sna tshogs lam du khyer dgos te /
NK016(ma)002:907: bsgrub mchog gsang ba'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK016(ma)002:908: skye bo'i yid rnams gsang phyir dang //
NK016(ma)002:909: gti mug mun pa gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK016(ma)002:910: dung dang mkhar rnga rdza rnga dang //
NK016(ma)002:911: cang te'u pi wang ka ko la //
NK016(ma)002:912: snyan par sgrogs pa'i rdzas rnams kun //
NK016(ma)002:913: sna tshogs 'byung pa'i rol mo ste //
NK016(ma)002:914: nyer rdzogs dus ni sbyar bar bya //
NK016(ma)002:916: gsum pa bro gar 'du 'phro'i yo byad ni /
NK016(ma)002:918: bro gar gyi skabs la rnal 'byor pho mo lhar
NK016(ma)002:919: gsal ba'i ngos nas bro dang gar byed dgos te
NK016(ma)002:920: / tshom bu tshogs bsgrub le'u bdun pa las //
NK016(ma)002:921: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kun //
NK016(ma)002:922: dbus nas shar phyogs kha bltas te //
NK016(ma)002:923: seng ge'i stabs su mchod par bya //
NK016(ma)002:925: rigs lnga la glu bro mi 'dra ba lnga gsung kyang /
NK016(ma)002:926: 'dir ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas rang nyid lha
NK016(ma)002:927: yab yum gyi nga rgyal gyis rkang pa'i bro dang
NK016(ma)002:928: lag pa'i gara gyi mchoda par byas te /
NK016(ma)002:929: de yang bro brdung ba dang gar byed pa'i dus
NK016(ma)002:930: de nyid na 'od kyis 'du 'phror byin gyis brlabs
NK016(ma)002:931: pa ni / 'od zer phar spros khams gsum gyi sems can la phog /
NK016(ma)002:933: sangs rgyas thams cad la phog thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)002:934: tshur 'dus dngos grub rnam gnyis ster bar bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:935: bro gar gyi dus su ma 'gags mi dmigs dbyer
NK016(ma)002:936: med byang chub sems su rtogs na dngosa grub mchoga
NK016(ma)002:938: de lta bu'i tshul du rnal 'byor pho mo kun gyis lus pad+ma gar gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK016(ma)002:940: sems ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas tshogs rdzas len pa bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:941: lnga pa +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad ni /
NK016(ma)002:942: rgya gar ba rnams kyi tshogs nang na byed par snang /
NK016(ma)002:945: bar rnams dngos su bsgral nas tshogs byed /
NK016(ma)002:946: phyag rgya mo mtshan nyid dang ldan pa yin na
NK016(ma)002:947: chags rtog lam du khyer nas sbyor mchod 'bul ba
NK016(ma)002:948: yin no // tshigs tsam gyi sbyor mchod ni /
NK016(ma)002:951: da ni sman mchod kyi don la gnyis te /
NK016(ma)002:954: dza gad bzung la sngar gyi gsang ba'i lha mo bzhis zhu bar bsam la 'di skad do //
NK016(ma)002:955: h'u cha lnga ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i bdag nyid lha bsgom pa'am /
NK016(ma)002:956: ye shes lnga'i rang gzugs rigs lnga'i dal gang yin
NK016(ma)002:957: pa de tshogs kyi gtso bo des ci mdzad na
NK016(ma)002:958: / gdul bya 'gro ba rnams kyis gang la gang 'dul de la der ston gyi don mdzad /
NK016(ma)002:959: khyad par du da res 'dir tshogs bsags pa'i zhing madzada pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:960: gtan tshigs de bas na h'u mdzad ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:961: h'u gisa thugsa dam bskang ba ni da res 'dir
NK016(ma)002:962: h'u ni bdud rtsi lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bo
NK016(ma)002:963: yin no // bdud rtsi lnga ma 'gag mi dmigs
NK016(ma)002:964: dbyer med pa byang chub sems su rtogs pa ni
NK016(ma)002:966: de la bdud rtsi lnga ngos bzung ba ni /
NK016(ma)002:967: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyis gtsang gtsog med pa lam du khyer ba /
NK016(ma)002:968: b+han+d+ha lcang lo dang bacasa pa'i snod pad+ma b+han+d+ha de ru /
NK016(ma)002:969: tshe 'dzina la bshad pa mang la mar khu la
NK016(ma)002:970: tshe 'dzin chang la pad+ma rak+ta la byang sems la
NK016(ma)002:971: da res 'dir byang sems la tshe 'dzin ces so
NK016(ma)002:972: // mchoga gi ste mi sha yin ste mchog chen me la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:973: damra chena dam pasa bskang ba ni rak+ta la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:974: rak+ta'i nad nas kyang yum gyi pad+ma'i zila tig yin ste /
NK016(ma)002:975: dri dang ni dri chen po rak+ta kha ni rak+ta gtso che ba la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:976: rdo rje slob dpon gyis rdo rje lasa kyi chu dang ni rdo rje slob dpon gyis dri chu'o //
NK016(ma)002:977: pany+tsa ni lnga a mri ta dang de rnams ni bdud rtsi lnga'o //
NK016(ma)002:979: sha lnga ni sman sgrubs kyi gtso bo yin par shes par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:980: sha lnga ni sha chena ste mi sha dang /
NK016(ma)002:981: mkha'a ldinga ste rma bya'i sha dang /
NK016(ma)002:982: shel sgong la 'dod pa mang ste /
NK016(ma)002:983: da res 'dir sman sna tshogs bsdus pa la 'brang rgyas ces bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:984: de lta bu'i gzugsa kyi tshogas la sogas kyis sgras /
NK016(ma)002:988: glang chen med na g.yag zhol po'i sha dang /
NK016(ma)002:989: rma bya med na bya wang sha dang /
NK016(ma)002:990: seng+ge med na khyi dkar sha dang de shang shang med na pha wam sha dang de rnams so //
NK016(ma)002:991: de lta bu'i sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa'i lnga tshan gyis sman chen lnga dang /
NK016(ma)002:992: da res 'chi med bdud rtsi lnga la tshe 'dzin pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:993: de rnams kun lhan gcig ru bsreb la byi la se zhes bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:994: sman sgrubs kyi dbang du byas na de rnams phyogs gcig tu spungs nas khrol bu'i bsgrub pa bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:995: de nas rkam phye'i bsgrub pa /
NK016(ma)002:997: dam pa rigs brgya'i sbyang ba /
NK016(ma)002:998: de nyid rigs lnga'i sbyang ba /
NK016(ma)002:999: gsang chen rigs gcig gi sbyang ba sogs dgos so //
NK016(ma)002:1000: sbyor dang zhes pa ni sman rtsa brgyad stong la sbyor ces so //
NK016(ma)002:1001: sgrol ba ni bam skye ba bdun pa la sgrol pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:1002: de lta bu'i sbyor ba dang /
NK016(ma)002:1003: sgrol ba'i badud rtsi mchoga nyid kyis /
NK016(ma)002:1004: h'u madzada ni tshogs kyi gtso bo la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1005: h'u gis ni sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i ngo bo ye shes lnga la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1006: thugas dam bskang bar mdzoda ni ma 'gags mi dmigs
NK016(ma)002:1007: dbyer med pa byang chub sems su rtogs nas sha
NK016(ma)002:1008: lnga bdud rtsi lnga lam du khyer ba'o //
NK016(ma)002:1009: rnal 'byor pho mo rnams kyi sarba pany+tsa a mri ta a la la ho /
NK016(ma)002:1011: de nas sman mchod la gnyis te /
NK016(ma)002:1012: sman gyi che ba brjod pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:1017: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga spang ma dgos par /
NK016(ma)002:1018: ranga byung 'dod nasa rnam par dag pa'i don ni /
NK016(ma)002:1019: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman yin no //
NK016(ma)002:1020: de la phyi'i sman rtsa brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)002:1029: nang bam gtsang ma blang ba'i rtsa ba brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)002:1030: pha'i rgyud las byung ba'i rtsa ba gsum ni /
NK016(ma)002:1034: ma'i rgyud las byung ba gsum ni /
NK016(ma)002:1038: pha'i rgyud lhag tshil bu dang /
NK016(ma)002:1039: ma'i rgyud lhag rkang mar dang gnyis sbyar ste brgyad do //
NK016(ma)002:1040: gsang ba rnam shes tshogs brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:1041: de med du mi rung ba'i rtsa ba brgyad dang gsum mo //
NK016(ma)002:1042: kha cig gis rtsa brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)002:1043: bdud rtsi lnga chu gtsang chang dang 'o ma gsum dang brgyad yin gsungs /
NK016(ma)002:1044: dri chen gyi rtsa ba brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)002:1045: bla ma grub thob kyi dri chen /
NK016(ma)002:1047: ku ku ra tsa'i dri chen /
NK016(ma)002:1048: me tog dri chen sbrang rtsi /
NK016(ma)002:1049: bya sna tshogs kyi dri chen /
NK016(ma)002:1050: nya sna tshogs kyis dri chen /
NK016(ma)002:1051: glang po che'i dri chen dang brgyad do //
NK016(ma)002:1052: byang chub sems kyi rtsa ba brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)002:1055: sha rus mthar phyin sen mo /
NK016(ma)002:1056: byang sems mthar phyin rus thig dang gdung sha ri ram /
NK016(ma)002:1057: byang sems mthar phyin ko ro tsa na /
NK016(ma)002:1059: byang sems ro brgyan gsang rten 'brel dang brgyad do //
NK016(ma)002:1060: mang sa'i rtsa ba brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)002:1072: yab kyi sna g.yas kyi khrag /
NK016(ma)002:1074: 'bras bu chen po bsgral ba'i khrag /
NK016(ma)002:1075: bya rgod khrag ste mu la brgyad do //
NK016(ma)002:1076: dri chu'i rtsa ba brgyad ni /
NK016(ma)002:1077: rgya mtsho sbu ba'i chu dang /
NK016(ma)002:1080: lan tsh+wa lhag tshun byang sems chu /
NK016(ma)002:1084: bam gyi sgang chu dang brgyad do //
NK016(ma)002:1086: seng+ge'i sha la sogs sder chags sna tshogs gis sha sna brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:1087: glang chen la sogs rmig pa kha brag sna tshogs gis sha sna brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:1088: rma bya'i sha la sogs 'dab chags sna tshogs kyi sha sna brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:1089: shang shang ti'u la sogs gdod pa can sna tshogs kyi sha sna brgyad do //
NK016(ma)002:1090: stong la sbyar ba'i sman ni sman rig sna tshogs bsdu ba la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1091: stong gi rnam grangs ni 'dir yi ge mang gi dogs pa'i phyir ma bris so //
NK016(ma)002:1092: rtsa brgyad stong sbyar gyi sman gyis rtsa ba ni sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga yin no //
NK016(ma)002:1093: de la sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga 'di nyams su
NK016(ma)002:1094: len pa la rnal 'byor pa rab kyis thug 'phrad
NK016(ma)002:1096: tha mas mos pa lam khyer gyis sgo nas nyams su len pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1097: rigas lnga'i dama tshiga lnga'i dngos kyi dngos gzhi yin pa la /
NK016(ma)002:1098: nang gi dgongs pa ye shesa lnga rdzogas grub pa'i rdzas yin pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1099: bdud rtsi kha dog gis rigs lnga yin te /
NK016(ma)002:1101: byang sems rdo rje sems dpa' dkar //
NK016(ma)002:1102: dri chen rnam par snang mdzad ser //
NK016(ma)002:1103: sha chen rin chen 'byung ldan sngo //
NK016(ma)002:1104: rak+ta snang ba mtha' yas dmar //
NK016(ma)002:1105: dri chu don yod grub pa ljang //
NK016(ma)002:1107: longs spyod nyer lnga'i dbang gzhung las /
NK016(ma)002:1108: dri chen bder gshegs dam rdzas te //
NK016(ma)002:1109: rdo rje sku yis dbang yang bskur //
NK016(ma)002:1110: byang chub sems kyi rdo rje yis //
NK016(ma)002:1111: rdo rje thugs kyi dbang yang sbyin //
NK016(ma)002:1113: rdo rje gsung gis dbang yang sbyin //
NK016(ma)002:1114: mam sa chen po rin chen rigs //
NK016(ma)002:1115: yon tan rin chen dbang yang sbyin //
NK016(ma)002:1116: gur gum las kyi dam rdzas te //
NK016(ma)002:1117: las mchog grub pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK016(ma)002:1119: sha lnga yang rigs lnga'i ngo bo yin pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1120: sha chen dag gi dam rdzas ni //
NK016(ma)002:1121: bde bar gshegs pa'i dam rdzas te //
NK016(ma)002:1122: glang chen sha'i dam rdzas ni //
NK016(ma)002:1123: rdo rje rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK016(ma)002:1124: rta sha dag gi dam rdzas ni //
NK016(ma)002:1125: rin chen rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK016(ma)002:1126: mkha' lding sha'i dam rdzas ni //
NK016(ma)002:1127: pad+ma rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK016(ma)002:1128: khyi sha dag gi dam rdzas ni //
NK016(ma)002:1129: las kyis rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK016(ma)002:1131: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga 'di rnams la chos mthun zhib tu ngo sprad rgyu yod kyang /
NK016(ma)002:1132: yi ge mang gi dog pa'i phyir ma bris so //
NK016(ma)002:1133: shes 'dod na gsal bkra'i 'grel pa nang du bkod nas yod /
NK016(ma)002:1134: de lta bu'i bdud rtsi sman 'di sangs rgyas la mchod na thugs dam bskang /
NK016(ma)002:1135: sems can la gtor na rgyud lnga'i semsa can kun bsgral ba'i sman chen 'di yin /
NK016(ma)002:1136: dug lnga sela ba'i bduda rtsi'i mchoga yang 'di yin no //
NK016(ma)002:1137: de'ang yul gang la phul zhe na /
NK016(ma)002:1138: mang ba'i tshad ni ji snyed sangsa rgyas thams cad
NK016(ma)002:1139: ste rgyal ba rigs lnga lta bu de lha gtso
NK016(ma)002:1140: bo rnams dang / byang chub semsa dpa'i tshogas chena
NK016(ma)002:1141: ni 'khor sems dpa' dang sems ma 'khor gyi tshul
NK016(ma)002:1142: bo rnams dang / 'dzin pa dang / sgo srung
NK016(ma)002:1143: gi tshul du khro bo khro mo mtha'a yasa pa
NK016(ma)002:1144: bo rnams dang / 'dzin pa dang / rnams dang
NK016(ma)002:1145: / tshig rkang 'di ni zhi ba'i lha tshogs shas
NK016(ma)002:1147: spyir gtso bo sangs rgyas kyi cha lugs /
NK016(ma)002:1148: bar gyis lha tshogs sras kyi tshul du 'dzin pa dang /
NK016(ma)002:1149: tha ma khro bo khro mo'i tshul du 'dzin pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1150: rgyud sde'i dkyil 'khor mtha' dag la yod par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1151: bka' sdod chos skyong ma mgon rnams ni nyi ma dang zer bzhin du /
NK016(ma)002:1152: yi dam gyi dal la ma dang mkha' 'gro rnams 'khor ba yin no //
NK016(ma)002:1153: ma mo mkha'a 'gro'i tshogas chena dang gzhan yang bka' sdod chos skyong ba'i srung ma mtha' dag dang /
NK016(ma)002:1154: lha dang lha mo gasnga ba yi mdzod 'dzin gyi
NK016(ma)002:1155: thugsa dam dbyingsa nyid bskul ba'i mchoga bdud rtsi 'di
NK016(ma)002:1156: yin / bdud rtsi 'di ni sngon gsang sngags pa
NK016(ma)002:1157: lam la zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis sha
NK016(ma)002:1158: lnga bdud rtsi lnga spang pa med pa ni dam
NK016(ma)002:1159: yin / tshig go // 'bras bu phyogsa bcu'i sangsa rgyas thamsa cad kyis /
NK016(ma)002:1160: sku gsunga thugsa kyi nganga nyid 'di yang sha lnga
NK016(ma)002:1161: bdud rtsi lnga spang ba med pa 'di yin no
NK016(ma)002:1162: // de lta bu'i sman 'di ni badga cag rnal
NK016(ma)002:1163: 'byor pas dada pasa 'bul lagas na bzhesa te ni
NK016(ma)002:1164: bdud rtsi'i mchod pa len pa la bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1165: kun tu dgyes mdzoda la ni bdud rtsi'i mchod pas mnyes par mdzod cig pa'o //
NK016(ma)002:1166: bdud rtsi phul ba'i yon tan la sku gsung thugs
NK016(ma)002:1167: kyi dngosa grub ni +aahmh'u gi tshul du badga rnal
NK016(ma)002:1168: 'byor pa la stsol bar bsgom ni 'bru mthun la
NK016(ma)002:1170: ta tha ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK016(ma)002:1176: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i chu 'di ni //
NK016(ma)002:1177: ye shes lnga la 'bul ba'i tshe //
NK016(ma)002:1178: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad mnyes //
NK016(ma)002:1179: dam can srung ma mchod pa'i tshe //
NK016(ma)002:1180: srung ma rnams kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK016(ma)002:1182: dngos grub rgya mtsho thams cad ster //
NK016(ma)002:1183: rnal 'byor bdag gis myong ba'i tshe //
NK016(ma)002:1184: dbang dang dngos grub yongs su rdzogs //
NK016(ma)002:1185: bdud dang bgegs la phog pa'i tshe //
NK016(ma)002:1186: lus sems thal ba rdul du rlog /
NK016(ma)002:1188: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i chu 'di ni //
NK016(ma)002:1189: mthong ngam thos sam reg pas kyang //
NK016(ma)002:1190: thams cad dbang phyug bdag gis thob //
NK016(ma)002:1191: e ma thabs chen khyad par che //
NK016(ma)002:1192: e ma ngo mtshar rmad du byung //
NK016(ma)002:1193: lta ba rmad byung ngo mtshar che //
NK016(ma)002:1194: spyod pa rmad byung ngo mtshar che //
NK016(ma)002:1195: nyon mongs ma spangs ngo mtshar che //
NK016(ma)002:1196: ye shes lnga rdzogs ngo mtshar che //
NK016(ma)002:1197: sku lnga lhun grub ngo mtshar che //
NK016(ma)002:1198: chos sku gcig la tha dad pa //
NK016(ma)002:1199: rigs lnga'i dngos grub 'dir thob bo //
NK016(ma)002:1200: yang dag 'chi med don snyams so //
NK016(ma)002:1202: des sman gyi che ba brjod pa de song nas /
NK016(ma)002:1204: lha mo rnams kyis nyi zla'i skyog thogs nas bdud rtsi lha tshogs la drangs pa'i tshul dang /
NK016(ma)002:1205: lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gur gyur nas lha tshogs rang rang gis gsol bar bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:1206: tshig shad kyi lag len la gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:1207: rtsa sde'i lugs la zhi khro phur gsum rang gzhung gis mchod pa mdzad /
NK016(ma)002:1208: kahthoga pa'i phyag len la sman mchod rgyas pa thos chog lugs 'di yin no //
NK016(ma)002:1209: de sman mchod kyi dngos grub len pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1210: tshogs zhing gi lha tshogs rnams kyis bdag rnal 'byor pho mo la zhal gyis phyogs /
NK016(ma)002:1213: dngos grub kyi tshig rnams brjod par bsam la /
NK016(ma)002:1214: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i sgor 'jug pa can gyi rnal 'byor pho mo khyod rnams ni /
NK016(ma)002:1215: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rigs can du nges na /
NK016(ma)002:1216: bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod pa'i dus su /
NK016(ma)002:1218: gtsog pa la ma sdang nas ro myong snang stong
NK016(ma)002:1219: gnyis med rdo rje'i lcer bsgom nas gsol na dngos
NK016(ma)002:1220: grub mchog sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)002:1222: de nas rdo rje slob dpon nas brtsam te /
NK016(ma)002:1223: thams cad kyi gnas gsum du thig le byas te /
NK016(ma)002:1224: de bzhin gshegs thams cad kyis yig 'bru gsum sku
NK016(ma)002:1225: gsung thugs kyis rdo rjer gyur nas bdag gi gnas
NK016(ma)002:1226: gsum du thim par bsam zhing /
NK016(ma)002:1228: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya sid+d+hi /
NK016(ma)002:1229: sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aak+ka sid+d+hi +aa sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK016(ma)002:1230: don la bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyis brjod par bsgom /
NK016(ma)002:1231: de nas tshogs las gzhung bzhin du bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1232: rtsa sde ba'i phyag len la drag po gsum bsgril la mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1233: khyad par du khong gi chos skyongs zhal gzigs pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK016(ma)002:1235: de nas rnal 'byor pho mo rnams kyi rol te /
NK016(ma)002:1236: ngag tu b+h+r+aum ha hi phata /
NK016(ma)002:1237: zhes brjod nas rang yi dam gyi thugs kar dbyings
NK016(ma)002:1238: kyi khrag 'thung sum cu gzhal yas khang dang bcas
NK016(ma)002:1239: pa bsgom / gzhan yang yi dam thams cad der bstim pa'i man ngag yin no //
NK016(ma)002:1243: rtsa gnas thams cad na dpa' bo dpa' mo'i tshogs /
NK016(ma)002:1244: de nas ljags rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i lte bar h'u dmar po /
NK016(ma)002:1245: zhal zas khams drug gi lha tshogs su gyur par bsgom zhing /
NK016(ma)002:1246: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la thim /
NK016(ma)002:1247: sgra'i lha mo snyan la thim /
NK016(ma)002:1248: dri'i lha mo shangs la thim /
NK016(ma)002:1249: ro'i lha mo ljags la thim /
NK016(ma)002:1250: reg bya'i lha mo sku la thim /
NK016(ma)002:1251: chos kyi lha mo thugs kar thim zhing rol lo //
NK016(ma)002:1252: dam pa bde bar gshegs pa'i zhal nas zos lhag
NK016(ma)002:1253: phyogs gcig tu bsdus nas lhag ma'i las che chung
NK016(ma)002:1254: gang rung bgyid cis gsungs pas /
NK016(ma)002:1256: sngar rgan rab rnams kyi mi byed pa ni phyag len 'chug pa 'dra bas /
NK016(ma)002:1257: bka' gsar rnying gter gsum gyi nang nas tshogs lhag bshad pas so //
NK016(ma)002:1259: zos lhag thams cad phyogs gcig tu bsdus nas sman raka sbreng la /
NK016(ma)002:1260: +aahmh'u gis byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1263: 'og dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs su bsam la /
NK016(ma)002:1264: lus kyis mdzes pa'i phyag rgya bca' /
NK016(ma)002:1265: ngag gis sgo nas e +aa ral+li ho /
NK016(ma)002:1267: badz+ra sa ma ya pheem pheem pheem ces brjod la /
NK016(ma)002:1268: de nas thugs kar lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK016(ma)002:1269: t+aaki r+aa tsa ces sogs brjod la /
NK016(ma)002:1270: rang gis thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal po phyung nas /
NK016(ma)002:1271: lhag mgron thams cad kyi thugs kar bzung nas dkyil 'khor gyi mu ran la 'khod par bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:1272: de nas mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i sngags tshang bar brjod pas /
NK016(ma)002:1274: mkha' 'gro ma suma cu rtsa gnyis /
NK016(ma)002:1275: dabnga mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK016(ma)002:1276: dam can bcu gnyis dregsa pa'i tshogs dang bcas pa /
NK016(ma)002:1281: pho nya druga cu rtsa bzhi la sogas pa dapala
NK016(ma)002:1282: chena po'i spyan sngar khasa blang dama bacasa pa la
NK016(ma)002:1283: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che bsrung bar
NK016(ma)002:1285: lhag ma'i mgrona du gyur pa /
NK016(ma)002:1286: tshogs lhag la dbang ba rnamas kyi zhal du e dam b+ha ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)002:1288: gnoda byed kyi bgegas thul tshiga /
NK016(ma)002:1289: chos spyod zab mo la bar chad du gcod pa'i rkyen bzlog cig /
NK016(ma)002:1290: chos byang chub bsgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK016(ma)002:1291: ces brjod la lhag ma skyong ngo //
NK016(ma)002:1292: lhag mgron rnams so so'i gansa su gshegas para bsgomsa /
NK016(ma)002:1293: rtsa sde ba'i phyag len la skabs 'dir bla ma
NK016(ma)002:1294: yi dam gyi spyan sngar gting bshags dang yig brgya
NK016(ma)002:1296: 'di'i dus su rang gi spyi bo'i dkar po las
NK016(ma)002:1297: 'od zer 'phros pas bde bar gshegs pa thams cad
NK016(ma)002:1298: kyi sku la mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul /
NK016(ma)002:1299: sku'i dam tshig chags nyams thams cad dag par bsgom /
NK016(ma)002:1300: rang gi mgrin pa'i +aahdamara po las 'od zer 'phros
NK016(ma)002:1301: pas bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung la
NK016(ma)002:1302: mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK016(ma)002:1303: rang gi ngag gi dam tshig chags nyams thams cad dag par bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:1304: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK016(ma)002:1305: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs la mnyes
NK016(ma)002:1307: rang gi yid kyi dam tshig chags nyams thams cad dag par bsgom mo //
NK016(ma)002:1308: rtsa sde ba'i phyag len la tshogs kyi bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK016(ma)002:1309: bkra shis gang zhig bde chen 'char byed cing //
NK016(ma)002:1310: mchog gsum 'phags pa'i bkra shis kun gyi gzhi //
NK016(ma)002:1311: bkra shis dngos grub yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK016(ma)002:1312: rje btsun mtshungs med bla mas bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1313: bkra shis gang zhig lha dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK016(ma)002:1314: lha yi bkra shis mngon par nyer thob cing //
NK016(ma)002:1315: bkra shis don gnyis legs par 'grub byed pa'i //
NK016(ma)002:1316: yi dam lha rnams kun gyis bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1317: bkra shis dpal ldan sku gsum rab brnyes shing //
NK016(ma)002:1318: ye shes rgya mtsho bkra shis mtha' yas pa //
NK016(ma)002:1319: bkra shis dbyings su 'gro rnams 'dren mdzad pa'i //
NK016(ma)002:1320: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1321: bkra shis gsung rab dri med rtogs pa yi //
NK016(ma)002:1322: don ldan chags bral bkra shis don dam chos //
NK016(ma)002:1323: bkra shis mchog gis sems can skyabs gyur pa'i //
NK016(ma)002:1324: dam chos rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyis bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1325: bkra shis sdom gsum rnam dag rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK016(ma)002:1326: thos btsun ting 'dzin bkra shis dbang 'byor bas //
NK016(ma)002:1327: bkra shis yid 'ong skye dgu'i dpal gyur pa'i //
NK016(ma)002:1328: dge 'dun dam pa rnams kyis bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1329: bkra shis mthar phyin dpal chen spyan lnga ru //
NK016(ma)002:1330: bstan pa bsrung bar khas blang bkra shis gang //
NK016(ma)002:1331: bkra shis mthu yis log 'dren tshar gcod pa'i //
NK016(ma)002:1332: chos skyong srung ma rnams kyis bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1333: bkra shis don gyis nyon mongs rnam dag cing //
NK016(ma)002:1334: nad rnams bkra shis stobs kyis zhi gyur nas //
NK016(ma)002:1335: bkra shis bden pa'i bgegs dpung 'joms byed de //
NK016(ma)002:1336: rnam pa kun du legs pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1337: bkra shis snyan pa'i ba dan kun khyab cing //
NK016(ma)002:1338: bsod nams chen po'i bkra shis rgyun chags nas //
NK016(ma)002:1339: bkra shis tshe dbang mi 'gyur rdo rje bzhin //
NK016(ma)002:1340: dpal 'byor phun sum tshogs pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1341: bkra shis mngon gyur rgyal ba'i bkra shis gyis //
NK016(ma)002:1342: bkra shis mchog tu basngagasa pa'i bkra shis gang //
NK016(ma)002:1343: bkra shis rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyis bkra shis shing //
NK016(ma)002:1344: bkra shis lhun gyi grub pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK016(ma)002:1345: rtsa sde ba'i bkra shis yid bzhin brtsegs pa 'di //
NK016(ma)002:1346: dbang dang rab gnas dang tshogs kyi dus su brjod par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1349: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK016(ma)002:1350: bsgom bzlas mchod bstod tshogs 'khor phul ba yi //
NK016(ma)002:1351: dge ba 'di yis bdag gzhan sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)002:1352: skyon bral yon tan ma lus rab rdzogs nas //
NK016(ma)002:1353: mthar thug sku lnga sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK016(ma)002:1354: tshogs kyi smon lam 'di ni pad 'byung gis gsungs so //
NK016(ma)002:1355: de nas tshogs zhing thams cad kyi thugs dgyes pa'i sgo nas sdig pa dag /
NK016(ma)002:1356: nyes pa tshang dam tshig chags nyams thams cad skongs ces pa'i gnang ba byin nas rang la thim /
NK016(ma)002:1357: tshogs zhing gi sku gsung thugs dang rang gi lus
NK016(ma)002:1358: ngag yid gsum dbyer med gcig tu 'dres par bsgom
NK016(ma)002:1359: la / ye d+har+m+aa tshar gcig brjod rab tu gnas par bya'o //
NK016(ma)002:1360: tshul 'di ni sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyi sgo nas
NK016(ma)002:1361: cho ga rnam dag phyag len phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK016(ma)002:1362: sgo nas brgyan pa yin no //
NK016(ma)002:1363: blun po gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhung gi khog ma chub pa 'ga' zhig gis /
NK016(ma)002:1364: 'di lta bu nga'i phyag len la mi byed bslad ma yin pa skad /
NK016(ma)002:1365: de la dgongs nas mkhas pas 'di ltar du gsungs /
NK016(ma)002:1366: tsu ta'i yul du phyin pa la /
NK016(ma)002:1367: rkang gnyis pa la mir mi rtsi //
NK016(ma)002:1369: yang cho ga rgyud dang mi mthun nas bslad nas thag rul snas 'bring rul /
NK016(ma)002:1370: 'brel pa med pa'i cho ga la dgongs nas //
NK016(ma)002:1371: lpa ba can gyis gling phran 'gar //
NK016(ma)002:1372: yan lag med pa'i skyon du bshad //
NK016(ma)002:1373: ces sa skya pan chen gyis gsungs so //
NK016(ma)002:1375: deng sang snyigs ma'i chos spyod lag len rnams 'di kho na red zin /
NK016(ma)002:1376: cho ga lhag chad la shor zin rnams rtsa ba nas mi rig 'dug /
NK016(ma)002:1377: gang zag chos kyi spyan can rnams kyi byed pa'i
NK016(ma)002:1378: gzhung lugs rnam dag la rjes su mi rung ba
NK016(ma)002:1379: ni snyigs ma'i sems can gyis chos lugs yin pas
NK016(ma)002:1380: so // rgya ston pa 'jam dbyangs kyi byin gyis brlabs pa'i gang zag dam pa yin yang /
NK016(ma)002:1381: gang zag phyogs 'dzin can rnams kyis rgya ston pas rgyal ba'i bstan pa bslad /
NK016(ma)002:1382: mang po yod pa nyung nyung byas //
NK016(ma)002:1383: nyung nyung yod pa mang po byas //
NK016(ma)002:1385: dpa' bo tshogs kyi rnam rol zhes bya ba'i tik+ka 'di ni /
NK016(ma)002:1387: pad 'byung gi tshogs kyi tik+ka chen po dang /
NK016(ma)002:1388: bla ma gong ma'i phyag len gyi tho yig rnams la /
NK016(ma)002:1389: rang gi nyer len gyi shes rab kyis dpyad nas tshogs spyi'i khog chings /
NK016(ma)002:1391: phyag len zhib tig su byas pa'i don ni /
NK016(ma)002:1392: bshes gnyen rnams kyis bskul ba'i ngor /
NK016(ma)002:1393: gsang sngags kyi rgyud gzhung rnams la blo kha cung zhig phyogs pa ye shes rgyal mtshan gyis /
NK016(ma)002:1394: dpal ldan kahthoga yang dgon du sbyar ro //
